Definition: an act or expression of criticism and censure
Example: he had to take the rebuke with a smile on his face
Synonyms: verb, communication, reproof, reproval, reprove, reprehension, reprehend, reprimand, criticism, an, act, or, expression, of, and, censure, he, had, to, take, the, with, a, smile, on, his, face
Category: noun.communication
